    "dom": "",
    "ris": "",
    "wid": ""
  },
  {
    "id": "42cea52d-f7c6-458d-9db9-260298cabebc",
    "sentence": "The staff continued to judge that uncertainty around the baseline projection was considerable and still viewed the risks as being influenced importantly by the potential macroeconomic implications of banking-sector developments, which could end up being more, or less, negative than assumed in the baseline.",
    "source": "minutes_20230614.html",
