    "dom": "",
    "ris": "",
    "wid": ""
  },
  {
    "id": "8d284927-b010-4cce-ae36-cb9147b352dc",
    "sentence": "The yield spreads of long-term Italian bonds over their German counterparts narrowed further, reaching the lowest level since March following agreement on the European Union (EU) Recovery Fund.",
