  },
  {
    "id": "f0723c09-d994-4c3d-822c-a7daa57cf65c",
    "sentence": "With respect to investment spending, several participants reported that business contacts had indicated that their firms were proceeding with existing investment projects but that heightened uncertainty was making them cautious about beginning new projects, especially larger ones; some smaller new investments or those with more certain payoffs were still being undertaken.",
    "source": "minutes_20250618.html",
    "doc_type": "minutes",
    "date": "20250618",
    "top": "",
    "ten": "",
    "sen": "",
    "dir": "",
    "com": "",
    "hor": "",
    "con": "",
    "dom": "",
    "ris": "",
    "wid": ""
  },
  {
    "id": "938f3106-8bf4-4c1a-a096-400d0cd47a87",
    "sentence": "Total PCE price inflation was only 0.5 percent over the 12 months ending in April, reflecting both weak aggregate demand in recent months and a considerable drop in consumer energy prices.",
